comment: Pierce (WAS) engages Millsap (ATL) but does not prevent him from freely moving.
Millsap (ATL) makes contact with Wall's (WAS) body and the contact affects his shot.
Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Beal (WAS) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Nene (WAS) does not push off of Horford (ATL).
Wall (WAS) makes incidental contact with Carroll (ATL) after he releases the shot.
Horford (ATL) jumps vertically and remains vertical throughout the contact with Wall (WAS).
Wall (WAS) makes contact with Schroder (ATL) while he is in legal guarding position but does not go through him.
Wall (WAS) makes contact with Schroder (ATL) but does not prevent him from freely moving.
Millsap (ATL) makes contact with Temple's (WAS) body and the contact affects his put back attempt.
Nene (WAS) makes contact with Teague (ATL) but does not prevent him from freely moving.
Nene (WAS) commits a take foul on Horford (ATL).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Pierce's (WAS) successful three-point field was released before time expired was overturned.
